      <title>中国股市有望延续刺激措施推动的涨势：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受北京方面支持措施的推动，中国相关股票有望进一步上涨，而随着投资者为进一步降息做准备，美国股市创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 22:39:40 GMT</pubDate>
